title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA/Falness/Gleeman
description: --Nordo is in for PA, we talk Aaron Rodgers and the 99 problems of the Purple, Kevin Falness comes in to talk Wild and make even more enemies, News to Nord, Aaron Gleeman joins to talk Twins and more.
